{
  "stem": "14251.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we first came to New York, New York City.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said, we're not going to live with all these deadbeats at the HIAS that were lying around, weren't learning the language, weren't--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "HIAS was one of the helping organizations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember what it stands for-- Hebrew something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother just went and got a job because she could speak some English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got a rented room in some fleabag place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she found one of her distant cousins who had come about 1940 via Holland somehow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was somewhat helpful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were not in any great shape, he and his wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had been in some camp and, and had been released, I think bought her way out because she was a, a well-known movie actress prior to that, had still some belongings that she could buy her way free out of the Camp Gurs, G-U-R-S.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a few months later, we decided we couldn't live here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother started to get sick again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to San Francisco, because some cousin of hers, the Shanghai people that had survived-- and these were all people I never saw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never knew any relative but my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, I was supposed to be-- you know, it's like being religious, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You just can't pull it off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By now I was-- came here-- 13.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I finally went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried it in New York, and that was a hopeless pit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she's always still pushing religion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we've got to get connected with quote, 'our people.' I didn't do well getting connected with our people, not in Berlin, not in New York, and not in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we were always the German, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
